From c778f11a37ca67866123ff5e71809bb958fcd8a5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mauricio Allende <mauricio@palta.io>
Date: Wed, 13 May 2026 21:42:38 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add minimal build tag to gate telemetry, docker, updates, and
 auth-daemon

Place OpenTelemetry/Prometheus/gRPC, Docker SDK, GitHub update check, and
PAM auth-daemon code behind a `minimal` build tag and supply no-op stubs
for the public API so the rest of the tree compiles unchanged. Lets
operators produce a stripped-down binary via `go build -tags=minimal`
that omits roughly two thirds of the linked code.
---
